The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v. Dennis McGuire, Appellant.

Motion to dismiss appeal denied; appellant to perfect the appeal for the October 1960 Term; appeal ordered to be placed on the calendar for October 10, 1960. The appellant’s time is enlarged accordingly. Nolan, P. J., Beldock, Ughetta, Kleinfeld and Christ, JJ., concur.
